  <p>Creates a new <link xref="GtkClutter.Actor"/> widget. This widget can be
used to embed a Gtk widget into a clutter scene.</p>  <p>This function is the logical equivalent of:</p>  <p>|[
ClutterActor *actor = gtk_clutter_actor_new ();
GtkWidget *bin = gtk_clutter_actor_get_widget (GTK_CLUTTER_ACTOR (actor));</p>  <p>gtk_container_add (GTK_CONTAINER (bin), contents);
]|</p>

